Requirements
------------

- spandsp spandsp-0.0.3_pre24.ebuild (get it from the Gentoo VoIP overlay)
  or from http://wojia.be/
- libedit-20061103.ebuild, this version fixes a bug of a header file installtion
- the openpbx.org-rc2.tar.gz, but you already have this
- you need to know how to put files in $PORTDIR_OVERLAY and $DISTDIR (see 
  Gentoo wiki for how to do that)
- activate $PORTDIR_OVERLAY in your make.conf

Pre-flight check
----------------

- put the spandsp ebuild in $PORTDIR_OVERLAY/media-libs/spandsp
- put net-misc in your $PORTDIR_OVERLAY
- put openpbx.org-rc2.tar.gz in your $DISTDIR
- cd $PORTDIR_OVERLAY/media-libs/spandsp
- ebuild spandsp-0.0.3_pre24.ebuild digest
- cd $PORTDIR_OVERLAY/net-misc/openpbx.org
- ebuild openpbx.org-rc2.ebuild digest

Installation
------------
- emerge -pv openpbx.org-rc2.ebuild
- set the USE flags you want
- emerge openpbx.org

You will find more information about how to run/configure CallWeaver.org on
http://www.CallWeaver.org/

Happy chatting